<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Upgrade Your {{year}} {{make}} {{model}} at Minimal Cost</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
        <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center;">
              {{#if dealershipLogo}}
              <img src="{{dealershipLogo}}" alt="{{dealershipName}}" style="max-height: 60px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              {{else}}
              <h2 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">{{dealershipName}}</h2>
              {{/if}}
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Hero Banner -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: {{brandSecondaryColor}}; padding: 25px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.3;">Time for an Upgrade?</h1>
              <p style="color: #ffffff; margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9;">Now may be the perfect time to make a move.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Main Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},
              </p>
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                Now may be the perfect time to upgrade. We have been tracking the value of your <strong>{{year}} {{make}} {{model}} {{trim}}</strong>, and right now your vehicle's market value is closely aligned with your remaining balance. That means you can move into something new at minimal out-of-pocket cost.
              </p>

              <!-- Value Comparison -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 25px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #fafafa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 25px;">
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="50%" style="padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-right: 2px solid #eeeeee;">
                          <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Current Market Value</p>
                          <p style="color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">{{marketValue}}</p>
                        </td>
                        <td width="50%" style="padding: 10px; text-align: center;">
                          <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Remaining Balance</p>
                          <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">{{payoffAmount}}</p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Breakeven Highlight -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 25px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #f9a825; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 20px 25px;">
                    <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                      <strong>What this means for you:</strong> Your vehicle's value and your remaining balance are nearly equal. You can trade in your current vehicle and transition into a newer model with little to no money out of pocket. This is one of the most cost-effective times to upgrade.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                Whether you are looking for the latest features, improved fuel efficiency, or simply a fresh start, our team is ready to walk you through every option and find the right fit for your budget.
              </p>

              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 30px;">
                Market values shift regularly, so this window may not last long. Let us help you take the next step.
              </p>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{dealershipWebsite}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 6px;">
                      See What Is Available
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0 0;">
                Or call us directly at <a href="tel:{{dealershipPhone}}" style="color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">{{dealershipPhone}}</a>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #333333; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <p style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 5px;">{{dealershipName}}</p>
              <p style="color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 5px;">
                <a href="tel:{{dealershipPhone}}" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">{{dealershipPhone}}</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 15px;">
                <a href="{{dealershipWebsite}}" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">{{dealershipWebsite}}</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #777777; font-size: 11px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;">
                Vehicle values are estimates based on current market data and are subject to in-person inspection and appraisal.
                If you no longer wish to receive these emails, please contact us to opt out.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
